title: Airdrop Special Edition Aavegotchi to NFT holders
body: I think this project need the support of NFT community. Airdroping some special edition NFT to NFT holders of certain type might bring them to get some interest into this game. Cryptopunks is for example the first NFT ever so these holders might help the community
author: 0xBcE3BD3b206946AbBe094903Ae2B4244B52fb4e9
